%%
%% docs/diagrams/deploy-pipeline.mmd
%% End-to-end CI/CD on push to main.
%%
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor dev as Developer
    participant gh as GitHub repo
    participant gha as GitHub Actions
    participant aws as AWS (us-east-1)
    participant ec2 as EC2 cncloud-dev-app-host
    participant rds as RDS Postgres

    dev->>gh: git push origin main

    Note over gha: deploy.yml triggers
    par 4 services in parallel (matrix)
        gha->>gha: mvn clean package
        gha->>gha: docker buildx --platform linux/amd64
        gha->>gha: push to Docker Hub<br/>tags: <sha> + latest
    end

    Note over gha: terraform-apply job (environment: production)
    gha-->>dev: ⏸ "Review pending deployments"
    dev->>gh: Approve production
    gha->>aws: AssumeRoleWithWebIdentity (OIDC)
    aws-->>gha: short-lived STS session
    gha->>aws: terraform apply

    Note over gha: ansible-deploy job
    gha->>aws: aws secretsmanager get-secret-value
    aws-->>gha: RDS credentials (no_log)
    gha->>ec2: scp docker-compose.aws.yml + .env (0600)
    gha->>ec2: docker compose pull + up -d --force-recreate
    ec2->>ec2: Spring Boot starts (lazy-init)
    ec2->>rds: JDBC connect (via secret)
    gha->>ec2: curl /actuator/health (retry until 200)
    gha-->>dev: ✅ Green
